Date: Thu, 23 Apr 2026 16:38:44 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] fix: 6 bugs - signup company name, dead links, chart crashes,
 settings profile, intent filter

1. Pass companyName to signUp action (was captured but never sent)
2. Fix dead chatbot links (test/conversations routes don't exist)
3. Add error handling for createChatbot when no ID returned
4. Fix analytics charts - transform object distributions to arrays
5. Add missing Intent filter dropdown on Leads page
6. Fix Settings profile - read from user_metadata instead of top-level

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
